terms.title: First Dimension
terms.Text: The physical component of our being that deals with the fundamentals of sport

terms.title: Second Dimension
terms.Text: The psychological component of our being that deals with the social/emotional/relational aspects of sport

terms.title: Third Dimension
terms.Text: The heart/spirit part of our being that acts as the executive center and functions as the will.

terms.title: Transformational Purpose
terms.Text: A coach's written statement that defines "WHY" he/she coaches and the intent to positively impact lives.
